{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01VySbUyDpdKHkqMCaskGeya","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"T3.4 is complete. Here's what was done:\n\n**`src/lib/gallery.ts`** — three additions:\n1. **Jitter**: `scheduleReconnect` now adds `Math.floor(Math.random() * base * 0.25)` ms on top of the capped exponential delay, spreading reconnects across clients.\n2. **Gap-fill**: `gapFill()` is called on every successful `ws.onopen`. It fetches the latest photos page and merges them into the store — deduplication by `id` ensures no duplicates.\n3. **Visibility pause/resume**: `scheduleReconnect` returns early if `document.visibilityState === 'hidden'`. A `visibilitychange` listener added in `start()` calls `openSocket()` directly when the tab becomes visible again. The listener is removed in `destroy()`.\n\n**`src/lib/gallery.test.ts`** — four new tests:\n- Jitter verification (deterministic via `Math.random` mock)\n- Gap-fill dedupe after reconnect\n- Visibility pause / resume\n- Updated timing in `reconnects with backoff` to mock `Math.random` for stable assertions\n\nAll 71 tests pass, typecheck clean, build succeeds. PR #9 merged into master."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":298,"cache_read_input_tokens":83394,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":298},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ed868337-1ce4-4888-9c5a-71786f4d3f4e","uuid":"25d5a5a9-c542-443c-b3cb-bb5d12908f59","request_id":"req_011CbRSwCnv1zMAtxUfCNfNN"}
